Leopard Gecko Care & Assist Feeding

LEOPARD GECKO CARE - Basic The leopard gecko, ( Eublepharis macularius), has been captive-bred in the United States for more than 30 years and is one of the most commonly kept lizards today. These hardy saurians come in a variety of colors, patterns and sizes. This is a great species for the home.
